{"data":{"content":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"805f5056-a8d7-5282-ad4f-061a2a11021c","html":"<h1 id=\"盒模型\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%92%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"盒模型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>盒模型</h1>\n<p>盒模型是DOM在渲染时采用的布局模型，可以通过box-sizing进行设置。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>content-box（W3C标准盒模型）:在标准盒子模型的情况下，width的长度就是内容的宽度，不包括padding、border</li>\n<li>border-box（IE盒模型）:在ie盒子模型的情况下，width的长度包括内容、padding、border</li>\n<li>pading-box（浏览器未实现）</li>\n<li>\n<p>margin-box（浏览器未实现）</p>\n<h1 id=\"bfc\"><a href=\"#bfc\" aria-label=\"bfc permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>BFC</h1>\n<p>BFC（block formatting context）是一个独立的渲染区，让处于BFC的内部元素与外部元素相互隔离，不会相互影响。</p>\n<h2 id=\"触发条件\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"触发条件 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>触发条件</h2>\n</li>\n<li>根元素</li>\n<li>float属性不为none</li>\n<li>position属性为absolute或fixed</li>\n<li>display属性为inline-block、flex、inline-flex、table、table-cell、table-caption</li>\n<li>\n<p>overflow属性不为visible</p>\n<h2 id=\"规则\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99\" aria-label=\"规则 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>规则</h2>\n</li>\n<li>内部元素box在垂直方向，一个接一个的放置</li>\n<li>两个box的垂直方向的margin会重叠</li>\n<li>BFC区域不会和float的元素区域重叠</li>\n<li>\n<p>计算BFC的高度时，浮动元素也会参与计算（不会浮动坍塌）</p>\n<h1 id=\"层叠上下文\"><a href=\"#%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87\" aria-label=\"层叠上下文 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>层叠上下文</h1>\n<p>分层显示机制，z-index</p>\n<h2 id=\"触发条件-1\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6-1\" aria-label=\"触发条件 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>触发条件</h2>\n</li>\n<li>根层叠上下文（html）</li>\n<li>position</li>\n<li>\n<p>css3属性:flex、transform、opacity、filter、will-change、-webkit-overflow-scrolling</p>\n<h2 id=\"层叠等级（优先级低到高）\"><a href=\"#%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%88%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E7%BA%A7%E4%BD%8E%E5%88%B0%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"层叠等级（优先级低到高） permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>层叠等级（优先级低到高）</h2>\n</li>\n<li>background/border</li>\n<li>z-index为负值</li>\n<li>块级元素</li>\n<li>浮动元素</li>\n<li>行内元素</li>\n<li>没有设置z-index到层叠上下文（z-index 0/auto）</li>\n<li>\n<p>z-index为正值</p>\n<h1 id=\"居中布局\"><a href=\"#%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80\" aria-label=\"居中布局 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>居中布局</h1>\n<h2 id=\"水平居中\"><a href=\"#%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD\" aria-label=\"水平居中 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>水平居中</h2>\n</li>\n<li>行内元素:text-align:center</li>\n<li>块级元素:margin:0 auto;</li>\n<li>absolute + transform</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex + justify-content:center</p>\n<h2 id=\"垂直居中\"><a href=\"#%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD\" aria-label=\"垂直居中 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>垂直居中</h2>\n</li>\n<li>line-height: height</li>\n<li>absolut + transform</li>\n<li>flex + align-items:center</li>\n<li>\n<p>table</p>\n<h2 id=\"水平垂直居中\"><a href=\"#%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD\" aria-label=\"水平垂直居中 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>水平垂直居中</h2>\n</li>\n<li>absolute + transform</li>\n<li>flex + justify-content + align-items</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"盒模型盒模型是DOM在渲染时采用的布局模型，可以通过box-sizing进行设置。content-box（W3C标准盒模型）:在标准盒子模型的情况下，width的长度就是内容的宽度，不包括padding、borderborder-box（IE盒模型）:在ie…","fields":{"slug":"/css/cssOutline"},"frontmatter":{"id":"https://MuRongJs.github.io/css/cssOutline","title":"css大纲","slug":"/css/cssOutline","date":"2019/3/18 17:26:20","headerImage":""}},"previous":null,"next":null}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"eb8e18f6-44b8-5840-a35f-a087f852f2c0","index":3}}